---
title: PowerShell Bootstrap Flow
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Trigger: code change / scheduled CI])
    Detect[Detect spec scope and changed files]
    Validate{Contract present?}
    Lint[Run module linter scripts]
    Gate{All gates pass?}
    Promote[Promote artefact / merge change]
    Block[Block + emit AppError ERR_SPEC_GATE_FAIL]
    Report[Update 99-consistency-report.md]

    Start --> Detect --> Validate
    Validate -- yes --> Lint --> Gate
    Validate -- no  --> Block
    Gate -- yes --> Promote --> Report
    Gate -- no  --> Block --> Report
